export const gradients = [
  'bg-gradient-to-br from-black via-red-900 to-black',
  'bg-gradient-to-br from-red-950 to-black',
  'bg-gradient-to-br from-black to-red-800',
  'bg-gradient-to-r from-red-900 via-black to-red-900',
  'bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-red-800 to-black',
  'bg-gradient-to-bl from-red-600 via-red-900 to-black',
];

export const accentColors = [
  'text-red-400',
  'text-white',
  'text-red-300',
  'text-yellow-400',
  'text-red-400',
  'text-red-200',
];
